# ChangeLog

Version 1.0.2

- Fixed "No image handler for type 15 defined" warning on macOS when taking a snapshot by initializing wxWidgets image handlers at startup.

Version 1.0.1

- Removed legacy migration code for old ip/port/path config format.
- Changed default snapshot folder to ~/Documents/FlashPrint/ (Documents\FlashPrint\ on Windows).

Version 1.0.0

- Initial Release.
